org.grobid.core.features
Class FeaturesVectorReference

java.lang.Object
  org.grobid.core.features.FeaturesVectorReference

public class FeaturesVectorReference
extends Object

Class for features used for reference identification in raw texts such as patent descriptions. It covers references to scholar works and to patent publications.

Author:
Patrice Lopez
